{"type":"message","id":"a1cff0f9","parentId":"7ba439d4","timestamp":"2026-06-07T04:34:35.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is right - there IS a Feishu doc for SOP v6.0! It's at https://my.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd\n\nBut looking at the SOP doc, it still says \"市场：越南(VN) + 泰国(TH)\" - which is the old version. The user wants me to update it to Vietnam only, and also wants a Feishu doc version.\n\nLet me tell the user that yes there IS a Feishu doc already, and offer to update it to remove Thailand since the user said TH should not be scanned.\n\n\nThe Feishu doc URL is https://my.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd with the title \"选品策略 6.0-越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略\", but it's currently showing Vietnam + Thailand when it should be Vietnam only per the user's instruction.","thinkingSignature":"1e64a5468943d3ab987a2037bba2801256617915e2a39a98c60de56628ed69c0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n飞书文档是有的，只是内容还没更新——SOP 里还写着越南+泰国两个市场。\n\n**SOP v6.0 飞书文档**：\nhttps://my.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd\n\n需要我把文档内容也改成\"只做越南\"吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3360,"output":278,"cacheRead":60320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63958,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780806870717,"responseId":"067427d7f6f90f40497e7f1af3cedd44"}}
