{"type":"message","id":"75f54fdb","parentId":"9126f546","timestamp":"2026-06-07T04:43:46.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying the SOP is missing a lot of field content, and there are fields that the SOP mentions but the Feishu bitable is missing. Let me check the current bitable structure vs what the SOP says should be captured.\n\nFrom the SOP:\n- 写入字段：商品标题、主图链接、TikTok销量数据、Shopee验证数据、1688采购价、毛利率评估、推荐等级（S/A/B级）、录入时间\n\nFrom the table data I saw, the fields include:\n- 商品名称 ✓\n- 站点 ✓\n- 选品来源 ✓\n\n\n- 采集状态 ✓\n- 三级类目 ✓\n- 售价（本地货币） ✓\n- 月销量 ✓\n- 利润率(%) ✓\n- 预估利润 ✓\n- 推荐等级 ✓\n- IP风险 ✓\n- 行动建议 ✓\n- 1688价格(CNY) ✓\n- 1688同款链接 ✓\n- 产品连接 ✓\n- 增长率 ✓\n- 日期 ✓\n\nThe table has most of the required fields covered, but I'm noticing some critical gaps like 主图链接, the Shopee verification data fields, and 录入时间 that the SOP explicitly mentions should be captured.","thinkingSignature":"e5d5b8d179fae8745ed012ba462d49b1d8d6837096d3dd90cb467664c8ec75b5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，我来看看 SOP 要求写入的字段和实际表格字段的差距：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a264d5aed53343d0bbb9621e","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table_field","arguments":{"action":"list","app_token":"AKppbA…QnZd","table_id":"tblHU2do30jzinJT","page_size":100}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3903,"output":353,"cacheRead":59808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64064,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780807419761,"responseId":"067429fcda776f6e011da6ffa5376395"}}
