{"type":"message","id":"53c9a4d1","parentId":"db7f4268","timestamp":"2026-06-07T04:43:56.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the actual bitable fields vs what the SOP says should be captured. Let me compare:\n\n**SOP v6.0 要求写入的字段：**\n1. 商品标题 ✓ (商品名称)\n2. 主图链接 → 缺失！只有 1688产品主图(附件)，没有 TikTok 主图链接\n3. TikTok销量数据 ✓ (月销量、增长率)\n4. Shopee验证数据 → 缺失！没有 Shopee 月销/评分/竞品数/差评关键词\n\n\n5. 1688采购价 ✓\n6. 毛利率评估 ✓ (利润率(%))\n7. 推荐等级（S/A/B级） ✓\n8. 录入时间 → 缺失！没有创建时间字段\n\nI also notice the SOP mentions the target bitable should have specific app and table IDs for logging products, which appears to be a separate tracking system from the main selection fields.\n\nLooking at the critical gaps, the main issues are the missing TikTok product image link field and the complete absence of Shopee validation data. I should flag these with the user and propose adding the necessary fields.\n","thinkingSignature":"e27efece6c5bffb26fae738f5af7480b7ce42c19186785dfd09023f81b8f4847"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对比 SOP 要求和实际表格字段，**缺失的关键字段**：\n\n| SOP 要求 | 实际表格 | 状态 |\n|---------|---------|------|\n| **TikTok 主图链接** | 空白（只有1688产品主图） | ❌ 缺失 |\n| **Shopee 月销量** | 空白 | ❌ 缺失 |\n| **Shopee 评分** | 空白 | ❌ 缺失 |\n| **Shopee 竞品数** | 空白 | ❌ 缺失 |\n| **Shopee 差评关键词** | 空白 | ❌ 缺失 |\n| **录入时间** | 只有\"日期\"（手动填） | ⚠️ 缺失自动时间 |\n| 1688采购价 | ✓ 有 | ✅ |\n| 毛利率 | ✓ 有 | ✅ |\n| 推荐等级 | ✓ 有 | ✅ |\n\n**核心问题**：流程跑的时候没有把 Shopee 验证数据和 TikTok 主图写入表格。\n\n要现在补上这些字段吗？我可以：\n1. 先在表格里新增缺失的字段\n2. 然后手动跑一次流程验证"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2567,"output":460,"cacheRead":63936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66963,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780807429320,"responseId":"06742a06192ed889f647a494034c909f"}}
