{"type":"message","id":"2ed03876","parentId":"8ee72ec3","timestamp":"2026-06-07T04:44:50.841Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the Feishu doc has been updated. Now let me summarize what was done.\n","thinkingSignature":"a538df1947eeda68f1dc66fbcd439d58060e7a5f37e5778f9cb58062bd8c2b5f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n飞书文档已更新：https://my.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd\n\n**改动总结：**\n\n| 改动项 | 原来 | 现在 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| 市场 | 越南+泰国 | **只做越南** |\n| 泰国 | 有 | ❌ 删除 |\n| 字段规范 | 写得模糊 | **20个字段逐一列出必填说明** |\n| 推荐等级 | S/A/B级 | **S/A/B/C四级**，判定标准明确 |\n| 行动建议 | 写得散乱 | **按等级对应固定文案** |\n\n核心变化是那张字段表——每个字段的类型、填什么、是否必填都写清楚了，下次 Cron 跑的时候我会按这个规范检查写入。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1960,"output":189,"cacheRead":71744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73893,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780807486060,"responseId":"06742a3efc97b768ac4361c3d7e08e89"}}
