{"type":"message","id":"8d0064a4","parentId":"65b93db9","timestamp":"2026-06-07T05:16:55.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No skill found for searxng. Let me also check the find-skills skill to see if there's a way to search for it.","thinkingSignature":"30242f04c5424517a994f9547c510d0bf5d68958a0b4283fc7076343957c56e5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n没有现成的 searxng skill。\n\nsearxng 是一个开源隐私搜索聚合引擎。你是想用它来替代 Google/百度做搜索吗？如果是的话，有几个思路：\n\n1. **直接调用 SearXNG API** — 很多公网 SearXNG 实例提供搜索 API，可以直接 curl 调用\n2. **本地部署 SearXNG** — 如果你有自己的 SearXNG 实例\n3. **让我搜一下有没有现成的 skill** — 用 find-skills 技能搜索\n\n你是想在选品流程里用它做什么？是想用 SearXNG 来搜索竞品信息、市场调研，还是其他用途？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29,"output":159,"cacheRead":76192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76380,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780809411365,"responseId":"067431c32752bf462f2e5a350ee2db8f"}}
